              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were produced by the T(d,n)4He",
                "reaction with an effective deuteron beam energy of",
                "134 keV and beam current of 230 mA. The tritium-",
                "titanium (T-Ti) target used in the generator was",
                "2.18 mg/cm2 thick. The neutron flux was monitored by",
                "a uranium fission chamber so that corrections could be",
                "made for small variations in the yield."
              ]
            }
